  "texts": [
    "And the longer it goes on, the more you fail in your attentional duties of friendship.",
    "At some point, you're just not really her friend at all.",
    "The problem here is that, even when you pay attention to your depressed friend, if you rely too much on algorithmic recommendation, you don't do so for your own moral reasons.",
    "Why, then, do you attend to her?",
    "As long as it's sufficiently likely to promote your engagement with online platforms, recommender systems will tend to direct your attention to her regardless of why you respond this way."
